# MinIO IAM split — content-control sibling pod's scoped user.
# ADR-048 PR-B7.
#
# Username (literal). Default keeps the chart, the bucket-init
# Job, and content-control's chart aligned.
#
# 1. Save as ./secrets/minio_content_control_user.txt.
# 2. Run `make k8s-bootstrap-secrets`. Lands at:
#    - Vault: kv/audittrace/minio/content_control (key: username)
#    - k8s Secret: <release>-minio-iam (content_control_user)
content_control
